# EDGE Performance Test | Locust

## Description
This project contains the performance tests for the following Edge resources 'Pipeline Core', 'Spark', etc.

## Setup
1. Install Python :
   ```bash
   sudo apt-get install python3
   ```
2. Install Locust:
   ```bash
   pip install locust
   ```
3. Navigate to each project folder:
   ```bash
   cd [projectFolder]
   ```

